Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好的看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为终有一天你也会继承这份使命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就是『调律』
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.02,0:01:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『调律』
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.92,0:02:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光? 『调律』是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将妖怪送往那个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个世界?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.53,0:02:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 爷爷 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:34.60,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,1000)}{\pos(320,340)}你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也并不是什么稀奇的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔带来见下面也是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 但是 也不仅仅是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊 因为大家都评价说很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想亲眼所见一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.64,0:02:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…你遇到的就只有那自称乱射魔的小兄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:02:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:02:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是谨慎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不露尾巴  那只狐狸混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狐狸？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有只喜爱恶作剧的狐狸在城镇周围徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 你不用太过于在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.28,0:03:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东铃 居住在樱真镇这段期间 要暂时约束你的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全信任曾让城镇陷于危险之中的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是我 还是这座城镇都不会如此宽容的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是去上学的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是找寻能寄住的打工地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边工作 自己挣取学费
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这些？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我引起了那么大的骚乱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是知道后才来这里的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是为妖怪而建的城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:03:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我还有公事在身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详细的事情就问秋名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了 我把秋名先生带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有段时间没见了吧 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然也来这里露个脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有很多的事情要忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是妖怪生活商讨所所长 比泉秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇上生活的全面安排都是由他那管理的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什么问题的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么人类会做这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是妖怪的城镇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被讨厌了呢 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.53,0:04:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么和人类的关系会如此亲近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:04:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城镇有它的规则所在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护妖怪的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在这个城镇住下的话 就得听秋名的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被『七乡』所包围的范围之内大致都张开了结界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看了地图就会了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上只需要记住\N过桥后就是安全的 那就没什么问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边是车站
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分的商店都聚集在那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.93,0:05:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都知道有很多的妖怪在 你也不用太在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医院在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是专门为妖怪而设立的 所以不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 这个也是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 车站前有银行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了吗 在车站前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说事务所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了吗 由我来带路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想早点赏花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱色遍染的城镇 一定相当美丽的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区长 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是『七乡』吗 去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那个必要 已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去元老院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得把城镇的吉祥物用狸怎么样 狸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会给人种被哄骗了的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比猪要好点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样说起来\N你听说炸猪排店有会笑的猪的图画没？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊 有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是打算去吃蒙古烤肉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但结界外面有只狐狸 去吃不成啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我也不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍 城镇的吉祥物用哺乳类可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊猫之类的不也很可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个可是猛兽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在着冷气的房间里像糟老头似的懒来懒去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来完全就像个懒虫的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实很凶暴的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给它取名叫 牛舌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.46,0:08:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是食材吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是挺悠哉 但貌似能看到某现实的未来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这概念才是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来的很晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了 桃华一直在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呀 言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉 被元老院给传召了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫铃的孩子来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是上次的那个『不死人』吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没来过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是有个公园的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找事务所
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道那个人类在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 对公务的怠慢也太随意了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位…不是人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？ 你是说恭助？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把角亮出来给你看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  去事务所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打电话给秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在妖怪的城镇 让人类当所长真是够奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实如此 我从前也是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那人的危机意识也太过薄弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谈论的问题的要点不是这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 现在眼前就有一个正在困惑中的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该也很清楚 他是城镇必不可少的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必不可少？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:10:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够『调律』的只有比泉家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『调律』？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将妖怪的灵魂送入另一个的世界\N也就是妖怪的世界能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就是『调律』
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为了解救在这个世界暴走的妖怪\N也只有这个方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用秋名的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是被称为解救吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在了 在了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃华 没有必要帮这种男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别称呼我为「这种男人」啊  妹控
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹控
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.63,0:10:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹控
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别躲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹控
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是杀了妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为是妖怪 所以杀了它也没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:11:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为对方不是人类 就可以这样开怀大笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名不是这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  是我解释的不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前爷爷也是这么说我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实也可以看成是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是不顺利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 是把她送回事务所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没有印章的话 签个名就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迁入申请只是个形式罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:11:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:12:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这公寓附近有人类居住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有两户人家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有其他地方可选了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我们也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.69,0:12:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是人类 也不都是坏人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是这镇上住着的人都已经习惯和妖怪为邻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 老在意这些的话 连学校都去不了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这点伤应该完全没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们妖怪不都很强的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准说人类的语言 说几句妖怪语来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…不要…不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:12:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类无论怎么伤害妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着妖怪难受也都若无其事一般
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不会有这样的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 我看起来也是那样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本也是人类 看起来像那类人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定有着「人类的时候真好」这样的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『花』
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为现在也不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀掉吗…很难回答啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 根据居民所述 是突然爆炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:13:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是由于妖怪的力量暴走所致
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.31,0:14:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的事可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有前例
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 再来做点愉快的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能 从未听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是照片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当事人原本就是一个拥有很强妖力的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其力量在瞬间爆发出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的 怎么可能暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当事人口述说 在力量爆发之前 身体发热 无法控制
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口述说？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.39,0:14:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被某种东西附身上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这么认为的 但却找不到任何痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会议中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.47,0:14:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  又发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:14:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我自己也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.23,0:15:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在自己未能察觉的情况下 妖力就暴走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请详细告诉我经过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才已经跟警察说明过了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你再说明一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助 秋名在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他打过电话 没人接
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象也没在事务所里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我绝对不要干消灭妖怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你所有背负的使命 终有一天你会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承受着那样的罪过\N正是因为你有着要保护的事物存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为比泉家之人 这是非做不可之事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在动摇什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校我也不会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:15:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是和姬约定好了的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为我不知道会同人类一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和人类一起生活的话 很快就会习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们认为没事 而我却很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是已经决定好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护城镇  就必须进行『调律』
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被说了几句 就变得如此心神不定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的决心就只有这点程度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有决心 但…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人称为杀人者 我也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护城镇 你的使命…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名你所做的并没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小在这城镇中长大 身为妖怪的我是如此坚信的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样都还不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的…我知道的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在事务所 在事务所发生了暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.19,0:16:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是铃 东铃的妖力正在暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍 布下结界 不要让人接近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言叶 恭助 先防止暴走造成更大的破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『笼』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『笼』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『笼』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这要怎么样才能阻止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来 我抑制的这段时间 你们快去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用『调律』的话 便能减轻妖力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃呢 要把她送走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『调律』
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实的呆在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.17,0:18:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是打算杀掉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要杀掉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.61,0:19:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 比泉家的人杀害过妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若无其事 毫无痛苦 一直都在…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.17,0:19:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好怕 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在内心却一直都明白「不能做这样的事」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是这样 如果这力量能保护他人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有坚信这力量是必须的妖怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『调律』
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来不是铃的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这家伙在操纵着妖怪的力量而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『调律』…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺努力的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越期待了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌妖怪的人类是不会做这样的事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…帖符的替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 你要喜欢那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.66,0:21:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说啦 别用哺乳类的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.20,0:21:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算用这当食物的名字你也这么认为？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.89,0:21:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛舌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.06,0:21:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驳回
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.48,0:21:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢一直以来的惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.97,0:21:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝宝兰店送餐来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.32,0:21:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叉烧面两份 馄饨面一份
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.02,0:22:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.19,0:22:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两千四百日圆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.04,0:22:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.98,0:23:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名表现的像主角一点吧
